Package ui

package ui
  • Class Summary
    Class
    Description
    BoxesPanel
    This is the class of the Center Panel : it's a GridLayout filled with MBoxPanel (it's basically the maze)
    ButtonPanel
    this is the button panel that allow the player to chose between arrival , departures..It's on the right It has 5 buttons (Departure, Arrival, Wall, Empty and Dimensions)
    MazeApp
    MazeApp is the Main class of the ui, sets visible the windowPanel
    MazeOptions
    MazeOption is the Jpanel on the left that can take actions on the maze it has 5 buttons : import, export, quit, solve and reboot
    MBoxPanel
    MBox Panel is the Panel that represents the MBox of the Maze.
    WindowPanel
    the windowPanel is composed of The boxesPanel(gridLayout of MBoxPanel) in the center, the MazeOptionsPanel on the left and the MazeButtonsPanel on the right
